**Help** | **Bot information**
`DUtils+` contains some random utilities, such as `calc`, `translate`, `sandbox` and so on.
The main purpose of this bot is to have many different utilities that may come in handy someday. For example, you can search for something in Google directly in Discord without opening browser, or, execute any code you want in safe sandbox (supports over 681 programming languages!)

